{"type":"message","id":"44eb5431","parentId":"fbf7a9e0","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:03:52.751Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit has finished creating the draft. Let me check what it wrote, and also I need to reply to 汀桑 about the draft content.\n\nBut wait - 汀桑 also said \"并且评价该数字恶臭等级\" at the end. Let me check the full conversation history. He said `/注册-恶臭数字 \"把输入的数字比如出生日期拆解为114514的组合\"` and in his next message (the yield interrupt), he said \"并且评价该数字恶臭等级\". \n\nActually looking more carefully at the yield interrupt message - it contains both the Spirit's completion event AND a follow-up message from 汀桑 saying \"并且评价该数字恶臭等级\". But the yield interrupt contains `[sessions_yield interrupt]` followed by conversation info metadata. The \"并且评价该数字恶臭等级\" seems to be 汀桑's message after the interrupt.\n\nSo he wants me to:\n1. Show the draft and ask for confirmation\n2. ALSO evaluate the \"恶臭等级\" of his number\n\nWait, which number? The last number he sent was 124863794. Or he might be referring to the concept in general.\n\nActually, looking at it again - the yield interrupt message has:\n- The Spirit's completion event \n- Then \"并且评价该数字恶臭等级\"\n\nThis is 汀桑 sending another message asking me to evaluate the \"恶臭等级\" of the number. Which number? Probably the last one he sent - 124863794.\n\nBut first let me check Spirit's draft output.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_SJ2OiwlhnsEPEVtu1riv8936","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/stench_number_function.md 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/stench_number_function.md 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":25570,"output":382,"cacheRead":11904,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":318,"totalTokens":37856,"cost":{"input":0.0035798,"output":0.00010696,"cacheRead":0.000333312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00