{"type":"message","id":"c486abe6","parentId":"ba385179","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:04:56.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑确认了，说\"对\"——就是要在输出里加\"恶臭等级\"评分。\n\n那我需要：\n1. 告诉汀桑我记下了这个需求，会加到功能定义里\n2. 走确认流程——让他确认\"确认注册？\"\n\n不过他已经说\"对\"了，是在确认我的问题，所以可以算确认了？\n\n等等，我再理一下流程：\n1. 我展示了draft内容\n2. 我问\"确认没问题我让Spirit标记完成\"\n3. 汀桑说\"对\"\n\nOK，他说\"对\"应该是确认没问题了。不过我也问了\"恶臭等级\"的问题，他说\"对\"——是对\"加恶臭等级评分\"这个说法的确认。\n\n好，那我不需要再问一次了，直接走注册完成的步骤：\n\nStep 1: 通知Spirit标记完成（⏳→✅）并更新文件\nStep 2: 我自己更新 trigger_prompt.md\nStep 3: Spirit同步文件到Son目录 + 更新functions_manifest.md\nStep 4: 通知Son建数据目录\n\n让我按AGENTS.md的流程来。先更新我自己这边的trigger_prompt.md。\n\n等一下，先看看trigger_prompt.md当前的样子。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zDi60i1eAWagqvRn2re43481","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5651,"output":318,"cacheRead":35200,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":261,"totalTokens":41169,"cost":{"input":0.0007911400000000001,"output":0.00008904,"cacheRead":0.0009855999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00186578}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780247092219,"responseId":"cd157fb3-9122-4928-a2b9-8fbdf48bdc7b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"311de217","parentId":"c486abe6","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:04:57.401Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_zDi60i1eAWagqvRn2re43481","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 命中表中触发语时直接 spawn Son，传 {function, action, params} 指令\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n> \n> **不再绕 Spirit。** 功能定义已迁移到 Son 的工作区，日常使用 Father → Son 直达。\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 | Son 指令 |\n|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) | — |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 | — |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md → Father → Son(同步功能定义) | — |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}` |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:pickup}` |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:list}` |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:reply, params:{id, content}}` |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | → Son | `{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | → Son | `{function:morningcourt, action:manual/set/disable, params:{...}}` |\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | → Son | `{function:album, action:save/list/view/search/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/画图` `画图` `/重画` | 画图 | → Son | `{function:draw, action:generate/regenerate/history, params:{...}}` |\n| `/作曲` `作曲` `/重作曲` `/作曲历史` | 作曲 | → Son | `{function:compose, action:generate/history/regenerate, params:{...}}` |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780247097400}}
{"type":"message","id":"49e57b76","parentId":"311de217","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:05:05.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I have the current trigger_prompt.md. Now I need to:\n\n1. Add a new row for the 恶臭数字功能\n2. Tell Spirit to mark the function as complete and copy it to Son's workspace\n\nLet me do both:\n\n1. First, update trigger_prompt.md with the new row\n2. Then tell Spirit to mark ✅ and sync to Son\n3. Tell Son to create data directory\n\nFor the trigger prompt entry, the trigger words are: `/恶臭` `/臭数字` (and maybe fuzzy matches like \"恶臭\" \"臭一下\")\n\nLet me also think about the Son指令 format. Looking at the existing entries:\n```\n{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}\n{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}\n```\n\nFor 恶臭数字, it would be something like:\n```\n{function:stench_number, action:stenchify, params:{number}}\n```\n\nLet me also update the function to include \"恶臭等级\" since 汀桑 confirmed that.\n\nActually, I should first:\n1. Update trigger_prompt.md (I do this myself)\n2. Spawn Spirit to mark ✅, update function file with 恶臭等级, copy to Son\n3. Spawn Son to create data dir\n\nLet me do step 1 and 2 in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_RXrITTY7Z2g1M5W2xDAh4383","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md","edits":[{"oldText":"| `/作曲` `作曲` `/重作曲` `/作曲历史` | 作曲 | → Son | `{function:compose, action:generate/history/regenerate, params:{...}}` |","newText":"| `/作曲` `作曲` `/重作曲` `/作曲历史` | 作曲 | → Son | `{function:compose, action:generate/history/regenerate, params:{...}}` |\n| `/恶臭` `恶臭` `/臭数字` `臭数字` | 恶臭数字 | → Son | `{function:stench_number, action:stenchify, params:{number}}` |"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"| `/作曲` `作曲` `/重作曲` `/作曲历史` | 作曲 | → Son | `{function:compose, action:generate/history/reg