{"type":"message","id":"22702382","parentId":"e989f528","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:12:53.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son的优化任务还在跑（2分31秒了）。汀桑说\"每次都会报这个错误\"——这可能是几个原因：\n\n1. **Subagent超时：** 每次我spawn Son/Spirit处理任务时，如果汀桑在这期间又发了消息，可能会导致session timeout错误，出现那个错误消息。\n2. **Gateway重启：** 我刚才重启了gateway，如果汀桑在那之后发了消息，路由可能还没完全恢复。\n3. **子任务执行时间长：** DeepSeek跑代码时可能会卡住或超时，导致汀桑看到错误。\n\n不过汀桑说的是\"每次\"——这可能是实际使用中会碰到的问题。常见的原因可能是：\n- 子agent执行时间超过30秒左右，汀桑在这期间发了消息，主session超时了\n- 或者Son执行过程中内存/资源问题\n\n我需要诚实地回答。最可能的原因是——每次我spawn Son干活的时候，汀桑如果紧接着发消息，我的session可能还在等Son回来，这时候系统会超时报错。\n\n跟汀桑说清楚这个情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"应该是超时的问题。每次我派Son干活的时候如果你紧接着发消息过来，我这边的session还挂着等Son回来，系统就先报错了。\n\n这段时间频繁spawn Son做任务，你连着发消息就容易撞上。Son跑完就没事了。\n\n现在Son还在优化那个算法，已经跑了2分半了。等他完事就好了😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2975,"output":304,"cacheRead":48384,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":229,"totalTokens":51663,"cost":{"input":0.00041650000000000004,"output":0.00008512000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0013547519999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018563719999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780247568749,"responseId":"9c89a974-e345-4a6b-89fa-19463f835f4f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a218fd6","parentId":"22702382","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:15:28.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son的超时了（5分钟，任务被杀了），没有真正完成优化。它只是说\"让我优化一下慢的部分\"就超时了。\n\n我需要处理这个情况——Son没能完成优化generate.py的任务。我可以：\n1. 重新spawn Son去做\n2. 或者自己看看脚本能不能跑通\n\n让我先看看当前generate.py的状态，看看Son写到什么程度了，然后决定怎么办。\n\n汀桑还在等结果，我得如实跟他说。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Son跑了5分钟，超时了，没写完😓 让我看看写到哪了。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2YPTYSSGsIWlPSdetbFa7951","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"wc -l ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py 2>/dev/null && echo \"---\" && head -80 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"wc -l ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py 2>/dev/null && echo \\\"---\\\" && head -80 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8810,"output":214,"cacheRead":42880,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":97,"totalTokens":51904,"cost":{"input":0.0012334000000000002,"output":0.00005992,"cacheRead":0.00120064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00249396}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780247724744,"responseId":"4acadd6f-eb50-4de2-bc9f-6d83dd0ce3fa"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a3d5802","parentId":"8a218fd6","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:15:28.668Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_2YPTYSSGsIWlPSdetbFa7951","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"989 /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py\n---\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n数字恶臭化生成器 — 通用搜索版 (v3)\n====================================\n使用 114514 系列数字池，通过通用 DFS/DP 搜索算法，\n自动拆解任意目标数字为恶臭风格数学表达式。\n\n约束：不产生值为 0 的中间结果。表达式中的数字尽量不含 0 数码位。\n运算符只用 + − × ÷，不出现 −− 双负号。\n\n搜索策略：\n  A - 直接加法分解（纯正数之和）\n  B - 114514 × k + r（基础乘法拆解，k 和 r 都分解）\n  C - 1145140 × k + r（大数乘法拆解）\n  D - 514 × a + 114 × b + r（双臭混合）\n  E - 14514 × k + r（近亲乘法变体）\n  F - 除法还原：(a × b) ÷ c + r \n  G - 114514 进制展开（学院派）\n\n用法：\n    python3 generate.py <数字>\n    python3 generate.py 20070521\n\n灵感源自 lab.magiconch.com 的数字恶臭化工具。\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys\nimport re\nimport math\nfrom functools import lru_cache\n\n# =====================================================================\n# 第一节：恶臭数字池\n# =====================================================================\n\n# 基础数集（不含 0 数码位）\nBASE_POOL = [1, 4, 5, 11, 14, 15, 51, 54]\n# 扩展数集（不含 0 数码位）\nEXT_POOL = [114, 514, 1145, 1451, 14514, 114514]\n# 巨型数（含 0 数码位的超级数，用于大数场景）\nMEGA_POOL = [1145140, 1919810, 1145141919810]\n\n# 全量池\nALL_POOL = sorted(set(BASE_POOL + EXT_POOL))\nALL_POOL_MEGA = sorted(set(ALL_POOL + MEGA_POOL))\n\n# =====================================================================\n# 第二节：辅助函数\n# =====================================================================\n\ndef has_digit_zero(n):\n    \"\"\"数字的十进制表示中是否含有 0 数码位\"\"\"\n    return '0' in str(abs(n))\n\ndef eval_expr(expr_str):\n    \"\"\"安全计算表达式值（替换 Unicode 数学符号为 ASCII）\"\"\"\n    s = expr_str.replace('×', '*').replace('−', '-').replace('÷', '/')\n    s = s.replace('＋', '+')\n    return eval(s)\n\ndef verify_no_zero_value(expr_str):\n    \"\"\"验证表达式计算不产生零值\"\"\"\n    if re.search(r'(?<!\\d)(\\d+)\\s*−\\s*\\1(?!\\d)', expr_str):\n        return False\n    if '÷ 0' in expr_str or '÷0' in expr_str:\n        return False\n    try:\n        return eval_expr(expr_str) != 0\n    except:\n        return False\n\ndef count_standalone(expr_str, target_num):\n    \"\"\"统计表达式中独立出现 target_num 的次数（非数字前缀）\"\"\"\n    pattern = r'(?<!\\d)' + str(target_num) + r'(?!\\d)'\n    return len(re.findall(pattern, expr_str))\n\ndef terms_sum(terms):\n    \"\"\"计算 [(sign, num), ...] 的代数和\"\"\"\n    return sum(v if s == '+' else -v for s, v in terms)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":70,"aggregated":"989 /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py\n---\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n数字恶臭化生成器 — 通用搜索版 (v3)\n====================================\n使用 114514 系列数字池，通过通用 DFS/DP 搜索算法，\n自动拆解任意目标数字为恶臭风格数学表达式。\n\n约束：不产生值为 0 的中间结果。表达式中的数字尽量不含 0 数码位。\n运算符只用 + − × ÷，不出现 −− 双负号。\n\n搜索策略：\n  A - 直接加法分解（纯正数之和）\n  B - 114514 × k + r（基础乘法拆解，k 和 r 都分解）\n  C - 1145140 × k + r（大数乘法拆解）\n  D - 514 × a + 114 × b + r（双臭混合）\n  E - 14514 × k + r（近亲乘法变体）\n  F - 除法还原：(a × b) ÷ c + r \n  G - 114514 进制展开（学院派）\n\n用法：\n    python3 generate.py <数字>\n    python3 generate.py 20070521\n\n灵感源自 lab.magiconch.com 的数字恶臭化工具。\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys\nimport re\nimport math\nfrom functools import lru_cache\n\n# =====================================================================\n# 第一节：恶臭数字池\n# =====================================================================\n\n# 基础数集（不含 0 数码位）\nBASE_POOL = [1, 4, 5, 11, 14, 15, 51, 54]\n# 扩展数集（不含 0 数码位）\nEXT_POOL = [114, 514, 1145, 1451, 14514, 114514]\n# 巨型数（含 0 数码位的超级数，用于大数场景）\nMEGA_POOL = [1145140, 1919810, 1145141919810]\n\n# 全量池\nALL_POOL = sorted(set(BASE_POOL + EXT_POOL))\nALL_POOL_MEGA = sorted(set(ALL_POOL + MEGA_POOL))\n\n# =====================================================================\n# 第二节：辅助函数\n# =====================================================================\n\ndef has_digit_zero(n):\n    \"\"\"数字的十进制表示中是否含有 0 数码位\"\"\"\n    return '0' in str(abs(n))\n\ndef eval_expr(expr_str):\n    \"\"\"安全计算表达式值（替换 Unicode 数学符号为 ASCII）\"\"\"\n    s = expr_str.replace('×', '*').replace('−', '-').replace('÷', '/')\n    s = s.replace('＋', '+')\n    return eval(s)\n\ndef verify_no_zero_value(expr_str):\n    \"\"\"验证表达式计算不产生零值\"\"\"\n    if re.search(r'(?<!\\d)(\\d+)\\s*−\\s*\\1(?!\\d)', expr_str):\n        return False\n    if '÷ 0' in expr_str or '÷0' in expr_str:\n        return False\n    try:\n        return eval_expr(expr_str) != 0\n    except:\n        return False\n\ndef count_standalone(expr_str, target_num):\n    \"\"\"统计表达式中独立出现 target_num 的次数（非数字前缀）\"\"\"\n    pattern = r'(?<!\\d)' + str(target_num) + r'(?!\\d)'\n    return len(re.findall(pattern, expr_str))\n\ndef terms_sum(terms):\n    \"\"\"计算 [(sign, num), ...] 的代数和\"\"\"\n    return sum(v if s == '+' else -v for s, v in terms)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780247728665}}
