{"type":"message","id":"7228ff9c","parentId":"5456d8a0","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:17:23.431Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_gCmgkCHHxY5tSY1GbrTH5320","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def generate(target):\n    \"\"\"\n    主入口：对目标数字执行恶臭拆解，返回格式化的输出行列表。\n    \"\"\"\n    results_lines = []\n\n    # 特殊处理：本身就是 114514\n    if target == 114514:\n        results_lines.append(f\"数字 114514 的恶臭拆解：\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n        results_lines.append(\"🤢 完美！114514 本身就是最臭的数字！\")\n        results_lines.append(\"恶臭等级：10/10 🏆 究极恶臭！\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n        results_lines.append(\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\")\n        results_lines.append(\"114514 = 114000 + 514\")\n        results_lines.append(\"114514 = 114 × 1000 + 514\")\n        results_lines.append(\"114514 = 514 × 222 + 114 + 114 − 5 + 1 − 1 + 4\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n        results_lines.append(\"🫵 你就是传说中的人？！\")\n        return results_lines\n\n    # 运行所有搜索策略\n    exprs = search_all_strategies(target)\n\n    if not exprs:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    top5 = select_top_expressions(exprs, 5)\n\n    if not top5:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    results_lines.append(f\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解：\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 最佳恶臭\n    best = top5[0]\n    best_expr, _, _, best_level, best_emoji, best_label, _ = best\n    results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭：\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {best_expr}\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{best_level}/10 {best_emoji} {best_label}\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 其他恶臭组合\n    if len(top5) > 1:\n        results_lines.append(\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\")\n        for item in top5[1:]:\n            expr, _, _, _, _, _, _ = item\n            results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    results_lines.append(\"--- \")\n    results_lines.append(\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\")\n\n    return results_lines\n\n\ndef generate_academic(target):\n    \"\"\"学院派兜底：当通用搜索找不到足够好的结果时使用\"\"\"\n    results_lines = []\n\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=898 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780247843430}}
{"type":"message","id":"a24d82e7","parentId":"7228ff9c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:17:32.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the flow now. The `generate()` function:\n1. Checks for 114514 special case\n2. Runs `search_all_strategies(target)`\n3. If no results, falls back to `generate_academic(target)`\n\nThe problem is that `search_all_strategies` for large numbers might return trivial identity results (like `(514×N)÷514`), which are then selected as \"best\" over the academic approach.\n\nThe fix should be: for large numbers (> 10^8 or similar), first try the academic approach, or skip the trivial identity patterns.\n\nBut actually, a simpler fix is:\n1. Remove the 10^9 limit\n2. In the `select_top_expressions` function or `generate` function, when the best result has a trivial pattern like `(514×N)÷514`, fall through to `generate_academic` instead.\n\nActually the simplest fix: In generate(), if target > 10^8, skip search_all_strategies and go directly to generate_academic.\n\nOr even simpler: just remove the 10^9 limit and the filtering that blocks 0-digit numbers (since the expression `114000` contains zero, it was already rejected... wait, the 114514 special case has `114000 + 514` which contains 0 digit - but that's only for target == 114514).\n\nLet me just:\n1. Remove the 10^9 limit (or raise to 10^18)\n2. For large numbers (> 10^8), prefer academic approach\n\nLet me make the changes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_rH0C7XTjGuUKfQvqkx8G3170","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    if target > 10**9:\n        print(\"🤢 数字太大了，暂时只支持 10 亿以内的数字\")\n        print(\"试试小一点的数字吧！\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    lines = generate(target)","newText":"    lines = generate(target)"},{"oldText":"    if not exprs:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    top5 = select_top_expressions(exprs, 5)\n\n    if not top5:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    results_lines.append(f\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解：\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 最佳恶臭\n    best = top5[0]\n    best_expr, _, _, best_level, best_emoji, best_label, _ = best\n    results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭：\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {best_expr}\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{best_level}/10 {best_emoji} {best_label}\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 其他恶臭组合\n    if len(top5) > 1:\n        results_lines.append(\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\")\n        for item in top5[1:]:\n            expr, _, _, _, _, _, _ = item\n            results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    results_lines.append(\"--- \")\n    results_lines.append(\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\")\n\n    return results_lines","newText":"    # 大数直接走学院派路线\n    if target > 10_000_000:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    if not exprs:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    top5 = select_top_expressions(exprs, 5)\n\n    if not top5:\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    # 检测最佳表达式是否为恒等式偷懒\n    best_expr, _, _, best_level, best_emoji, best_label, _ = top5[0]\n    if best_level <= 6 and re.search(r'\\(\\d+ × target\\) ÷ \\d+', best_expr.replace(str(target), 'target')):\n        return generate_academic(target)\n\n    results_lines.append(f\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解：\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 最佳恶臭\n    results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭：\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {best_expr}\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{best_level}/10 {best_emoji} {best_label}\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 其他恶臭组合\n    if len(top5) > 1:\n        results_lines.append(\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\")\n        for item in top5[1:]:\n            expr, _, _, _, _, _, _ = item\n            results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    results_lines.append(\"--- \")\n    results_lines.append(\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\")\n\n    return results_lines"}]},"parti