{"type":"message","id":"c94134fb","parentId":"54dfac43","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:18:04.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, the fix works but ALL numbers > 10M are going to the academic route, including 20070521 which the DFS should have been able to handle. The 10M threshold is too low.\n\nLet me raise it to 10^9 or even remove the threshold and just use the identity detection.\n\nActually, the issue is more nuanced:\n- 20070521 (~2×10^7) - should work with DFS, and it did before\n- 124863794 (~1.2×10^8) - mixed results\n- 25826985564 (~2.5×10^10) - too large\n- 1687565695657863579 (~1.6×10^18) - way too large\n\nLet me change the threshold to something like 10^9 (1 billion), which will allow 20070521 to go through DFS but route the larger ones to academic. Also, the 124863794 which is ~1.2×10^8 could go either way, but the academic output is actually decent for it: `114514 × 1090 + 43534`.\n\nActually for 124863794, the DFS found a good solution before: `114514 × (514 + 514 + 51 + 11) + 43534` with 9/10 rating. That's better than the academic \"114514 × 1090 + 43534\" with 5/10.\n\nSo the threshold should be higher, maybe 10^9 (1 billion), which allows numbers up to 1 billion to try DFS first. Let me also keep the identity detection for cases where DFS is lazy.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"10M太低了，20070521也被截了。改成10亿，让中小数走DFS，大数走学院派。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jlZi3jlM0HIz6UO7uaev8027","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    # 大数直接走学院派路线\n    if target > 10_000_000:\n        return generate_academic(target)","newText":"    # 超大数直接走学院派路线（10亿以上）\n    if target > 1_000_000_000:\n        return generate_academic(target)"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"    # 大数直接走学院派路线\\n    if target > 10_000_000:\\n        return generate_academic(target)\",\"newText\":\"    # 超大数直接走学院派路线（10亿以上）\\n    if target > 1_000_000_000:\\n        return generate_academic(target)\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":356,"output":525,"cacheRead":59904,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":345,"totalTokens":60785,"cost":{"input":0.000049840000000000004,"output":0.00014700000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001677312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001874152}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780247879365,"responseId":"15cf2f36-afa6-476e-a660-9216f85fba12"}}
