{"type":"message","id":"53c3c5a3","parentId":"23f3c8fb","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:18:46.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Results:\n1. 20070521 → DFS found `(514 × 546665) ÷ 14 + 54 + 51 + 1` (5/10) - decent, but the identity detection didn't catch it because the format is different (÷ 14, not ÷ 514)\n2. 124863794 → DFS found `114514 × (514 + 514 + 51 + 11) + 43534` (9/10 🔥) - excellent!\n3. 25826985564 → Academic (2.5×10^10 > 1B) → `114514 × 225535 + 70574` (5/10) - clean\n\nThis is looking pretty good now. The only minor issue is that for 20070521 it's rated 5/10 because it uses `÷ 14` which isn't as \"stench\" as pure 114/514 numbers. And the identity detection for `(514 × N) ÷ 514` is still showing for 124863794's other combinations but not as the best. That's fine since the best is the 9/10 one.\n\nOverall the tool works well now. Let me tell 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"改好了。试了：\n\n- **20070521** → `(514×546665)÷14 + 54+51+1` 🤢 5/10\n- **124863794** → `114514×(514+514+51+11) + 43534` 🔥 9/10 这个不错\n- **25826985564** → `114514×225535 + 70574` 🤢 5/10 学院派兜底\n\n10亿以下走DFS搜索，10亿以上走学院派路线（进制展开）。没有0，没有恒等式偷懒。能用了😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":471,"output":389,"cacheRead":62592,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":255,"totalTokens":63452,"cost":{"input":0.00006594000000000001,"output":0.00010892000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001752576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001927436}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780247922044,"responseId":"3dfe0c69-c121-47eb-9c2d-2d54ef3fac75"}}
