{"type":"message","id":"53363b0a","parentId":"2ff52b2a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:18:54.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说得有道理。他的意思是：\n1. 对于大数字，可以先用114514不断去除（取模），拆成 N = 114514 × k + r 的形式\n2. 这样k和r都变小了\n3. 再把小的k和r分别进行恶臭拆解\n4. 组合起来就是一个完整的恶臭表达式\n\n这其实就是递归的思路——114514进制展开的增强版。原来的学院派只做了一层 `114514 × k + r`，但k和r本身也可以继续拆。\n\n让我改一下generate_academic或者给大数加一个递归策略。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啧 说得对。递归拆就完了——先用114514取模拆出商和余数，商和余数各自再恶臭化，拼起来。改一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_MOHHDMdIqU7evEvYVw7A5040","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"def generate_academic\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -n \\\"def generate_academic\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":15227,"output":235,"cacheRead":48256,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":129,"totalTokens":63718,"cost":{"input":0.0021317800000000002,"output":0.0000658,"cacheRead":0.001351168,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003548748}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780247930725,"responseId":"a24d7d9f-7abf-481a-afbc-56acb81d8ae6"}}
