{"type":"message","id":"4c09cf69","parentId":"b8a5255c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:19:00.310Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_lshxpmP43Fs4IimdJigZ7574","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def generate_academic(target):\n    \"\"\"学院派兜底：当通用搜索找不到足够好的结果时使用\"\"\"\n    results_lines = []\n    results_lines.append(f\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解（学院派）：\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 114514 进制展开\n    base = 114514\n    n = target\n    parts = []\n    i = 0\n    ok = True\n    while n > 0:\n        d = n % base\n        if d == 0:\n            ok = False\n            break\n        if has_digit_zero(d):\n            ok = False\n            break\n        if i == 0:\n            parts.append(f\"{d}\")\n        elif i == 1:\n            parts.append(f\"{d} × 114514\")\n        else:\n            parts.append(f\"{d} × 114514^{i}\")\n        n //= base\n        i += 1\n\n    if ok and parts:\n        expr = \" + \".join(reversed(parts))\n        level, emoji, label, _ = rate_expression(expr)\n        results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr}\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{level}/10 {emoji} {label}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n    else:\n        k = target // 114514\n        r = target % 114514\n        expr2 = f\"114514 × {k} + {r}\"\n        level2, emoji2, label2, _ = rate_expression(expr2)\n        results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr2}\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{level2}/10 {emoji2} {label2}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 附加\n    k514 = target // 514\n    r514 = target % 514\n    expr3 = f\"514 × {k514} + {r514}\"\n    if not expr_has_bad_patterns(expr3):\n        results_lines.append(\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr3}\")\n\n        k114 = target // 114\n        r114 = target % 114\n        expr4 = f\"114 × {k114} + {r114}\"\n        if not expr_has_bad_patterns(expr4):\n            results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr4}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    results_lines.append(\"--- \")\n    results_lines.append(\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\")\n\n    return results_lines\n\n\ndef main():\n    if len(sys.argv) < 2:\n        print(\"用法: python3 generate.py <数字>\")\n        print(\"示例: python3 generate.py 20070521\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    try:\n        target = int(sys.argv[1])\n    except ValueError:\n        print(\"❌ 请输入有效的正整数\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    if target <= 0:\n        print(\"🤢 请输入正整数。0 和负数不能进行恶臭拆解。\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    lines = generate(target)\n    for line in lines:\n\n[6 more lines in file. Use offset=987 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780247940309}}
{"type":"message","id":"32841392","parentId":"4c09cf69","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:19:10.961Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑的思路是：对一个大数，先用114514取模拆成 N = 114514 × k + r，然后对k和r分别递归做恶臭拆解（如果k或r本身也很大，继续递归）。这样就不会出现 `114514 × 225535 + 70574` 这种半成品，而是能把225535和70574也拆成114514风格的表达式，叠多层递归。\n\n让我重写 generate_academic 函数。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TYZot9ypsGYdktJkQThK4560","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py","edits":[{"oldText":"def generate_academic(target):\n    \"\"\"学院派兜底：当通用搜索找不到足够好的结果时使用\"\"\"\n    results_lines = []\n    results_lines.append(f\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解（学院派）：\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 114514 进制展开\n    base = 114514\n    n = target\n    parts = []\n    i = 0\n    ok = True\n    while n > 0:\n        d = n % base\n        if d == 0:\n            ok = False\n            break\n        if has_digit_zero(d):\n            ok = False\n            break\n        if i == 0:\n            parts.append(f\"{d}\")\n        elif i == 1:\n            parts.append(f\"{d} × 114514\")\n        else:\n            parts.append(f\"{d} × 114514^{i}\")\n        n //= base\n        i += 1\n\n    if ok and parts:\n        expr = \" + \".join(reversed(parts))\n        level, emoji, label, _ = rate_expression(expr)\n        results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr}\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{level}/10 {emoji} {label}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n    else:\n        k = target // 114514\n        r = target % 114514\n        expr2 = f\"114514 × {k} + {r}\"\n        level2, emoji2, label2, _ = rate_expression(expr2)\n        results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr2}\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{level2}/10 {emoji2} {label2}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 附加\n    k514 = target // 514\n    r514 = target % 514\n    expr3 = f\"514 × {k514} + {r514}\"\n    if not expr_has_bad_patterns(expr3):\n        results_lines.append(\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\")\n        results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr3}\")\n\n        k114 = target // 114\n        r114 = target % 114\n        expr4 = f\"114 × {k114} + {r114}\"\n        if not expr_has_bad_patterns(expr4):\n            results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr4}\")\n        results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    results_lines.append(\"--- \")\n    results_lines.append(\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\")\n\n    return results_lines","newText":"def _recurse_stench(n, depth=0):\n    \"\"\"递归恶臭拆解：用114514反复取模拆分，直到每个部分都小于114514可直拆\"\"\"\n    if depth > 3:\n        return str(n)\n    if n < 114514:\n        # 小数字尝试用DFS拆\n        if n in ALL_POOL or n < 20:\n            return str(n)\n        # 用 514/114 拆一层\n        for divisor in [514, 114, 14514]:\n            if n > divisor:\n                k = n // divisor\n                r = n % divisor\n                if r != 0 and not has_digit_zero(r):\n                    k_part = _recurse_stench(k, depth+1)\n                    r_part = _recurse_stench(r, depth+1)\n                    return f\"{divisor} × {k_part} + {r_part}\"\n        return str(n)\n    \n    k = n // 114514\n    r = n % 114514\n    \n    if r == 0 or has_digit_zero(r):\n        # 余数有0，换个拆法\n        k = n // 514\n        r = n % 514\n        if r != 0 and not has_digit_zero(r):\n            k_part = _recurse_stench(k, depth+1)\n            r_part = _recurse_stench(r, depth+1)\n            return f\"514 × {k_part} + {r_part}\"\n        return str(n)\n    \n    k_part = _recurse_stench(k, depth+1)\n    r_part = _recurse_stench(r, depth+1)\n    return f\"114514 × {k_part} + {r_part}\"\n\n\ndef generate_academic(target):\n    \"\"\"学院派兜底：递归用114514反复取模拆解大数\"\"\"\n    results_lines = []\n    results_lines.append(f\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解（学院派）：\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    expr = _recurse_stench(target)\n    level, emoji, label, _ = rate_expression(expr)\n    results_lines.append(\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"{target} = {expr}\")\n    results_lines.append(f\"恶臭等级：{level}/10 {emoji} {label}\")\n    results_lines.append(\"\")\n\n    results_lines.append(\"--- \")\n    results_lines.append(\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\")\n\n    return results_lines"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"def generate_academic(target):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"学院派兜底：当通用搜索找不到足够好的结果时使用\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    results_lines = []\\n    results_lines.append(f\\\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解（学院派）：\\\")\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n\\n    # 114514 进制展开\\n    base = 114514\\n    n = target\\n    parts = []\\n    i = 0\\n    ok = True\\n    while n > 0:\\n        d = n % base\\n        if d == 0:\\n            ok = False\\n            break\\n        if has_digit_zero(d):\\n            ok = False\\n            break\\n        if i == 0:\\n            parts.append(f\\\"{d}\\\")\\n        elif i == 1:\\n            parts.append(f\\\"{d} × 114514\\\")\\n        else:\\n            parts.append(f\\\"{d} × 114514^{i}\\\")\\n        n //= base\\n        i += 1\\n\\n    if ok and parts:\\n        expr = \\\" + \\\".join(reversed(parts))\\n        level, emoji, label, _ = rate_expression(expr)\\n        results_lines.append(\\\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(f\\\"{target} = {expr}\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(f\\\"恶臭等级：{level}/10 {emoji} {label}\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    else:\\n        k = target // 114514\\n        r = target % 114514\\n        expr2 = f\\\"114514 × {k} + {r}\\\"\\n        level2, emoji2, label2, _ = rate_expression(expr2)\\n        results_lines.append(\\\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(f\\\"{target} = {expr2}\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(f\\\"恶臭等级：{level2}/10 {emoji2} {label2}\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n\\n    # 附加\\n    k514 = target // 514\\n    r514 = target % 514\\n    expr3 = f\\\"514 × {k514} + {r514}\\\"\\n    if not expr_has_bad_patterns(expr3):\\n        results_lines.append(\\\"💩 其他恶臭组合：\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(f\\\"{target} = {expr3}\\\")\\n\\n        k114 = target // 114\\n        r114 = target % 114\\n        expr4 = f\\\"114 × {k114} + {r114}\\\"\\n        if not expr_has_bad_patterns(expr4):\\n            results_lines.append(f\\\"{target} = {expr4}\\\")\\n        results_lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"--- \\\")\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\\\")\\n\\n    return results_lines\",\"newText\":\"def _recurse_stench(n, depth=0):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"递归恶臭拆解：用114514反复取模拆分，直到每个部分都小于114514可直拆\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    if depth > 3:\\n        return str(n)\\n    if n < 114514:\\n        # 小数字尝试用DFS拆\\n        if n in ALL_POOL or n < 20:\\n            return str(n)\\n        # 用 514/114 拆一层\\n        for divisor in [514, 114, 14514]:\\n            if n > divisor:\\n                k = n // divisor\\n                r = n % divisor\\n                if r != 0 and not has_digit_zero(r):\\n                    k_part = _recurse_stench(k, depth+1)\\n                    r_part = _recurse_stench(r, depth+1)\\n                    return f\\\"{divisor} × {k_part} + {r_part}\\\"\\n        return str(n)\\n    \\n    k = n // 114514\\n    r = n % 114514\\n    \\n    if r == 0 or has_digit_zero(r):\\n        # 余数有0，换个拆法\\n        k = n // 514\\n        r = n % 514\\n        if r != 0 and not has_digit_zero(r):\\n            k_part = _recurse_stench(k, depth+1)\\n            r_part = _recurse_stench(r, depth+1)\\n            return f\\\"514 × {k_part} + {r_part}\\\"\\n        return str(n)\\n    \\n    k_part = _recurse_stench(k, depth+1)\\n    r_part = _recurse_stench(r, depth+1)\\n    return f\\\"114514 × {k_part} + {r_part}\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef generate_academic(target):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"学院派兜底：递归用114514反复取模拆解大数\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    results_lines = []\\n    results_lines.append(f\\\"🤢 数字 {target} 的恶臭拆解（学院派）：\\\")\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n\\n    expr = _recurse_stench(target)\\n    level, emoji, label, _ = rate_expression(expr)\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"📿 最佳恶臭（学院派）：\\\")\\n    results_lines.append(f\\\"{target} = {expr}\\\")\\n    results_lines.append(f\\\"恶臭等级：{level}/10 {emoji} {label}\\\")\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"--- \\\")\\n    results_lines.append(\\\"🫵 你也是恶臭人了！\\\")\\n\\n    return results_lines\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":829,"output":1500,"cacheRead":63744,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":98,"totalTokens":66073,"cost":{"input":0.00011606000000000001,"output":0.00042,"cacheRead":0.0017848319999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023208919999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780247940596,"responseId":"d2ca63db-bf62-4e57-9e9d-8154ec4f0683"}}
