{"type":"message","id":"efa547ea","parentId":"00450c8f","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:24:00.962Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说得对，所有特定功能（不仅仅是恶臭数字）都可以用这个模式：我收到触发词 → 建一个cron在后台跑 → 结果直接推给用户，而不是我一直挂着等Son回来。这样就不会有session超时报错的问题了。\n\n不过这是一个比较大的架构调整，涉及trigger_prompt.md里的逻辑。今晚太晚了，还是明天再说吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啧 确实。所有注册功能都可以这么搞——我收指令 → 建条一次性cron → 回你一句\"在搞了\" → 完事直接推你\n\n不用傻等着，你该发啥发啥，不卡。\n\n不过今晚先到这吧😏 困了🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":567,"output":146,"cacheRead":71168,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":80,"totalTokens":71881,"cost":{"input":0.00007938,"output":0.00004088,"cacheRead":0.001992704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002112964}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780248237307,"responseId":"ffbe3230-37ab-40f7-96fd-a1d23389b2fd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a53b5cc","parentId":"efa547ea","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:24:42.160Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"给我起来工作！","timestamp":1780248279422}}
{"type":"message","id":"cf7a3135","parentId":"6a53b5cc","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:24:51.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑让我起来工作，说要改cron模式。好吧，既然他喊了我就动起来。\n\n他的意思是要改所有已注册功能的路由方式，从现在的\"spawn Son等结果\"改成\"I spawn Son的cron → 回\"在搞了\" → Son跑完直接推结果给用户\"。\n\n这需要改trigger_prompt.md里的处理逻辑，以及整个路由流程。\n\n但等等，这个改动不小。让我想想怎么搞：\n\n1. 每个功能触发时，我不再`spawn Son`等结果，而是建一个一次性cron\n2. cron的delivery设为announce，推给汀桑的QQ\n3. 我直接回一句\"在搞了\"就完事\n\n但这意味着我需要改每个功能的处理逻辑。不太现实全部改，可以先让Son那边有个通用的机制。\n\n不过仔细想想，cron模式下Son的session需要能访问汀桑的QQ来直接推结果。这需要配置好delivery。\n\n或者更简单的方式：不是用cron，而是让Son直接通过sessions_send推结果给我，我再转给汀桑？不对，那还是会卡我。\n\n其实真正的问题是：每次我spawn Son时，如果汀桑紧接着发消息，我的session会挂起等Son回来，结果系统超时报错。\n\n解决方案：\n1. spawn Son时用`mode: \"run\"`（已经是在用了）\n2. 我不yield等它，直接回汀桑\"在搞了\"\n3. Son完成后自动推结果过来\n\n实际上我现在的流程就是spawn + yield。如果我不yield，直接回复汀桑，然后等Son的completion event来了再处理——但问题是completion event是作为新消息到我的session里的，我能在不yield的情况下收到completion event吗？\n\n或者更简单：我每次spawn Son后，不yield等待，直接回复汀桑\"在搞了\"，然后等completion event来了我再把结果转发给汀桑。\n\n问题是我现在都是sessions_yield等待，这样会话就卡住了。如果不yield，我直接回复，那Son回来时会有个completion event到我session里，我就可以处理了。\n\n让我试试这个方式。\n\n但汀桑说的是\"用cron\"的方式。那就用cron吧。建一个一次性cron，payload是agentTurn让Son执行任务，delivery设成announce推给汀桑。\n\n我来试试这个方案，先改恶臭数字功能的路由方式做个实验。\n\n不对，现在应该是直接跟汀桑说怎么搞，看看他的想法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"……行吧行吧😮‍💨\n\n不过这个改动不小——所有已注册功能都得改路由逻辑。我先拿恶臭数字试水，搞通了再批量改别的。\n\n思路是这样：\n1. 你说 `/恶臭 114514`\n2. 我建一条一次性cron → Son跑 → 结果直接推你QQ\n3. 我秒回\"在臭了😏\" 不卡你\n4. 你随便继续发消息，不报错\n\n试试？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xNkoNVwfex52GqH4jbr58321","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":512,"output":704,"cacheRead":71296,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":541,"totalTokens":72512,"cost":{"input":0.00007168,"output":0.00019712,"cacheRead":0.001996288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002265088}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780248282191,"responseId":"e445bbb9-0fc9-4d4c-820e-fc10391b94ea"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c3d3b28","parentId":"cf7a3135","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:24:53.314Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_xNkoNVwfex52GqH4jbr58321","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 命中表中触发语时直接 spawn Son，传 {function, action, params} 指令\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n> \n> **不再绕 Spirit。** 功能定义已迁移到 Son 的工作区，日常使用 Father → Son 直达。\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 | Son 指令 |\n|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) | — |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 | — |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md → Father → Son(同步功能定义) | — |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}` |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:pickup}` |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:list}` |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:reply, params:{id, content}}` |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | → Son | `{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | → Son | `{function:morningcourt, action:manual/set/disable, params:{...}}` |\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | → Son | `{function:album, action:save/list/view/search/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/画图` `画图` `/重画` | 画图 | → Son | `{function:draw, action:generate/regenerate/history, params:{...}}` |\n| `/作曲` `作曲` `/重作曲` `/作曲历史` | 作曲 | → Son | `{function:compose, action:generate/history/regenerate, params:{...}}` |\n| `/恶臭` `恶臭` `/臭数字` `臭数字` | 恶臭数字 | → Son | `{function:stench_number, action:stenchify, params:{number}}` |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780248293313}}
{"type":"message","id":"e852c7b2","parentId":"5c3d3b28","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:25:00.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The key insight is: I need to change the processing path from \"→ Son\" to \"→ cron → Son → push to user\" for functions that take a while to execute.\n\nBut actually, the issue is simpler than I thought. The problem is that I use `sessions_yield` to wait for Son, which blocks my session. Instead, I should:\n\n1. spawn Son with `mode: \"run\"` \n2. NOT yield - immediately reply \"在搞了😏\"\n3. When Son's completion event arrives as a new message in my session, I forward the result to 汀桑\n\nBut wait, there's a problem: Son's completion event comes as a system event to my session, not as a QQ message. I need to somehow forward it.\n\nActually, looking at the docs more carefully, when a subagent completes, its result is sent to my session as a user message by the runtime. So I can:\n1. Spawn Son\n2. Reply to 汀桑 \"在搞了😏\" (don't yield)\n3. Later, when Son's completion event arrives as a new message, I forward the result\n\nBut the issue is - between step 2 and step 3, if 汀桑 sends another message, my session might process that message before Son's completion event arrives. And if there's no completion event handler, I just process 汀桑's next message normally.\n\nAlternatively, the cron approach would work cleanly:\n1. Create a one-shot cron with payload.kind=\"agentTurn\" that runs Son\n2. Set delivery to announce with 汀桑's channel\n3. Reply \"在搞了😏\"\n\nThis way Son's output goes directly to 汀桑 as a push notification, completely bypassing me.\n\nLet me try this approach for the stench_number function first. Let me update the trigger_prompt.md to indicate the new path, then when /恶臭 comes in, I'll create a cron job instead of spawning Son.\n\nActually, I should just test it first. Let me build a simple approach:\n\nFor /恶臭:\n1. Extract the number from the message\n2. Create a one-shot cron with agentId=son, payload as an agentTurn\n3. Set delivery to announce with channel=qqbot, to=汀桑\n4. Reply \"在臭了😏\"\n\nLet me try this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2ZY0AQaFjPovOOvR1tQ06673","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"test-stench-cron","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-31T17:30:00Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"测试：这是cron推送的恶臭数字结果。汀桑说改成cron模式，Son跑完结果直接推过来不卡主session。当前目标数字：114514","timeoutSeconds":120},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"deleteAfterRun":true,"enabled":false}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\": \"test-stench-cron\", \"schedule\": {\"kind\": \"at\", \"at\": \"2026-05-31T17:30:00Z\"}, \"payload\": {\"kind\": \"agentTurn\", \"message\": \"测试：这是cron推送的恶臭数字结果。汀桑说改成cron模式，Son跑完结果直接推过来不卡主session。当前目标数字：114514\", \"timeoutSeconds\": 120}, \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\", \"delivery\": {\"mode\": \"announce\", \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot1\", \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"}, \"deleteAfterRun\": true, \"enabled\": false}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":820,"output":731,"cacheRead":72448,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":495,"totalTokens":73999,"cost":{"input":0.00011480000000000001,"output":0.00020468000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0020285439999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023480239999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780248293630,"responseId":"155d4ac6-07a2-431f-bcd0-f42d0a9edbfc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab53b1b6","parentId":"e852c7b2","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:25:03.002Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_2ZY0AQaFjPovOOvR1tQ06673","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"3ce8f390-be71-45fd-ac62-3c283f22af83\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"test-stench-cron\",\n  \"enabled\": false,\n  \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1780248302252,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780248302252,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"at\",\n    \"at\": \"2026-05-31T17:30:00.000Z\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"测试：这是cron推送的恶臭数字结果。汀桑说改成cron模式，Son跑完结果直接推过来不卡主session。当前目标数字：114514\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n    \"accountId\": \"bot1\",\n    \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {}\n}"}],"details":{"id":"3ce8f390-be71-45fd-ac62-3c283f22af83","agentId":"father","name":"test-stench-cron","enabled":false,"deleteAfterRun":true,"createdAtMs":1780248302252,"updatedAtMs":1780248302252,"schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-31T17:30:00.000Z"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"测试：这是cron推送的恶臭数字结果。汀桑说改成cron模式，Son跑完结果直接推过来不卡主session。当前目标数字：114514","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780248302998}}
{"type":"message","id":"19e436cb","parentId":"ab53b1b6","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:25:15.831Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the cron creation API works. The delivery mode \"announce\" with channel=qqbot, to=汀桑's QQ id, accountId=bot1 should push the result directly to 汀桑's QQ.\n\nNow I need to think about how to make the cron actually run the stench_number algorithm. The cron's payload is an agentTurn which will create an isolated Son session. The isolated Son session needs to:\n1. Run generate.py with the target number\n2. Output the result\n\nBut wait, the cron I created has `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"` - this means it will run as an isolated session for the agent I specify. But the agent I specified in the cron is \"father\" (the default for my session). I think I need to use `agentId: \"son\"` in the cron, or use the sessionTarget differently.\n\nActually, looking at the cron schema more carefully:\n- `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"` means it creates an ephemeral isolated session\n- The agent for this session would be... the agent that owns the cron? Which is \"father\"\n\nHmm, I need Son to run the task, not Father. Let me think about this differently.\n\nOption 1: I spawn Son as a subagent, and Son itself creates the cron to push results\nOption 2: The cron's agentTurn runs in Son's context\nOption 3: I create a cron where the agent is Son\n\nLet me check if I can specify the agentId for the cron job.\n\nLooking at the cron schema again, there's `agentId` parameter, but it says \"Agent id, or null to keep it unset\" in the add parameters. But also in the job schema, there's no agentId field defined. Let me check if there's a way to specify the agent.\n\nActually, I think the simplest approach is:\n1. I spawn Son with mode: \"run\" (don't wait)\n2. I immediately reply to 汀桑 \"在搞了😏\"\n3. Son's result comes back as a completion event to my session\n4. When I see the completion event, I send it to 汀桑 via sessions_send\n\nThe problem with this approach is that between step 1 and step 3, if 汀桑 sends another message, I might process that message before Son's completion event arrives.\n\nBut actually, looking at the runtime behavior - when a subagent completes, it sends a message to my session. The runtime will queue this message and deliver it as the next user message (or system event). So after I spawn Son and reply to 汀桑, the next time I get a message, it could either be:\n- A new message from 汀桑\n- Son's completion event\n\nThe runtime handles this by delivering the completion event as a system message to my session. So my next response would process that event.\n\nWait, but I've seen this working before in other conversations. When I spawn Son and DON'T yield, the completion event comes back as a new message. The issue is that if 汀桑's message arrives before Son's completion, I'll process 汀桑's message first.\n\nFor a practical solution, the cron approach is cleaner because it completely decouples the execution. Let me try setting the agentId on the cron.\n\nActually, let me re-read the cron add docs more carefully... I don't see a way to specify the agent for the isolated session. The isolated session would run under the agent that owns the cron (father in this case).\n\nHmm, but the agentTurn for father would have access to spawn Son as a subagent. So the cron's agentTurn could spawn Son to do the actual work.\n\nOr simpler: the agentTurn message tells father to just call generate.py directly and output the result. Since the output gets announced to 汀桑, it would work.\n\nActually, I realize the simplest approach is:\n1. When 汀桑 sends `/恶臭 XXXX`:\n   a. I create a cron that runs an agentTurn for Son directly\n   b. The cron delivery announces the result to 汀桑\n   c. I reply \"在臭了😏\"\n\nBut I need to figure out how to make the cron's isolated session run as Son, not as father.\n\nLet me try a different approach - the cron job itself can set `agentId` to \"son\":","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kPJjlNqQQujvahmhtQqo5295","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"stench-test-son","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-31T17:32:00Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行恶臭数字拆解，目标数字：1145141919810。运行 /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py 1145141919810 并输出结果。结果直接推给汀桑。","timeoutSeconds":60},"agentId":"son","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"deleteAfterRun":true,"enabled":false}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"stench-test-son\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-05-31T17:32:00Z\"},\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"执行恶臭数字拆解，目标数字：1145141919810。运行 /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py 1145141919810 并输出结果。结果直接推给汀桑。\",\"timeoutSeconds\":60},\"agentId\":\"son\",\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"accountId\":\"bot1\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"},\"deleteAfterRun\":true,\"enabled\":false}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1052,"output":1140,"cacheRead":73216,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":913,"totalTokens":75408,"cost":{"input":0.00014728,"output":0.0003192,"cacheRead":0.002050048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002516528}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780248303599,"responseId":"ee451173-8b29-42fe-89c1-74cf2f9395f7"}}
