{"type":"message","id":"b6e13848","parentId":"501652f3","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:25:22.014Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_QwNdZ8tYYunKDoxFCWqr8460","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"enqueued\": true,\n  \"runId\": \"manual:7dae6b14-6fb7-4a59-8b52-c1534601c65a:1780248320995:1\"\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"enqueued":true,"runId":"manual:7dae6b14-6fb7-4a59-8b52-c1534601c65a:1780248320995:1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780248322012}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d6ce8c8","parentId":"b6e13848","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:25:33.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job has been triggered. It will execute Son with the task, and the result will be announced directly to 汀桑's QQ. This confirms the mechanism works.\n\nNow I need to design the actual workflow:\n\n1. When 汀桑 sends `/恶臭 <number>`:\n   - Extract the number\n   - Create a one-shot cron with:\n     - agentId: \"son\"\n     - payload: agentTurn message to run generate.py\n     - delivery: announce to 汀桑's QQ\n     - deleteAfterRun: true\n   - Reply to 汀桑: \"在臭了😏\"\n\n2. The cron runs Son, Son executes generate.py, and the output is pushed directly to 汀桑's QQ via announce.\n\nThis completely bypasses any waiting on my end.\n\nBut I should also figure out how to handle all other registered functions the same way. For now, let me start with just the stench_number function as a proof of concept, then we can expand.\n\nActually, the issue is coming up with the right prompt for Son. For stench_number, the task is:\n\"执行恶臭数字拆解，目标数字：{number}。运行 /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/stench_number/generate.py {number} 并输出结果。结果直接推给汀桑（sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204）。\"\n\nBut I want to make this more general. Let me think about it.\n\nActually for now, let me just tell 汀桑 the cron approach works for delivering directly to his QQ, and we can start with /恶臭 as the test case.\n\nLet me delete the test cron (it was set to deleteAfterRun so it should auto-delete after running).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"通了。cron直接跑Son，结果推到你QQ上，我不卡中间了。你看一下应该收到了吧？\n\n流程这样：\n1. 你说 `/恶臭 数字` → 我回\"在臭了😏\" → 建cron跑Son → 结果直接推你\n2. 你随便继续发消息，不卡不报错\n\n拿恶臭数字试水，通了再批量改别的功能。搞不搞？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":121,"output":477,"cacheRead":75776,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":378,"totalTokens":76374,"cost":{"input":0.00001694,"output":0.0