, task: \\\"{...}\\\")\\n  │   Step 2: sessions_yield 等结果\\n  │   Step 3: 转话给用户\\n  │\\n  └─ ⏰ cron（耗时操作）──────────\\n      Step 1: 回用户\"在搞了😏\"\\n      Step 2: 建一次性cron\\n        cron.add({\\n          name: \\\"功能名-参数\\\",\\n          schedule: {kind: \\\"at\\\", at: \\\"now+1s\\\"},\\n          payload: {kind: \\\"agentTurn\\\", message: \\\"执行任务...\\\", timeoutSeconds: 120},\\n          agentId: \\\"son\\\",\\n          delivery: {mode: \\\"announce\\\", channel: \\\"qqbot\\\", accountId: \\\"bot1\\\", to: \\\"用户QQ\\\"},\\n          deleteAfterRun: true\\n        })\\n      → Son 跑完结果直接推用户，不经过我\\n```\\n\\n⚠️ cron模式注意：\\n- 删除cron时要调整delivery.to指向对应用户的QQ\\n- timeoutSeconds 根据任务复杂度设，画图/作曲给长一点\\n- 管理功能（菜单/注册/删除）不走这两套，我自己处理\\n\\n**不再呼叫 Spirit。** 日常使用 I／O 路径缩短为：Father → Son → Father/用户。\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":355,"output":702,"cacheRead":82688,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":83745,"cost":{"input":0.0000497,"output":0.00019656,"cacheRead":0.002315264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002561524}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780248468747,"responseId":"a6503df5-1c94-44e2-b5b1-2816b90eb03e"}}
