{"type":"message","id":"8c83edf6","parentId":"db7808ec","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:28:32.462Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_TBdQPRPcT3ciLADJ4qf93265","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 3.3 调用已注册功能流程（两套路由）\n\n```\n触发: trigger_prompt.md 命中非 /菜单 /注册 /删除 的触发词\n\n→ 查 trigger_prompt.md「模式」列：\n  │\n  ├─ ⚡ 直连（秒回）─────────────\n  │   Step 1: spawn Son\n  │     sessions_spawn(agentId: \"son\", task: \"{...}\")\n  │   Step 2: sessions_yield 等结果\n  │   Step 3: 转话给用户\n  │\n  └─ ⏰ cron（耗时操作）──────────\n      Step 1: 回复用户```\n触发: session 收到格式为 [morningcourt] sender_id=xxx, trigger briefing generation 的消息\n\nStep 1: 识别模式\n  → 消息以 [morningcourt] 开头 → 早朝官 cron 触发\n  → 提取 sender_id\n\nStep 2: spawn Son\n  → sessions_spawn(\n      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: '{\"function\":\"morningcourt\",\"action\":\"manual\",\"params\":{\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}'\n    )\n\nStep 3: 等 Son 结果\n  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 主动话题推送\n\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头（见下方 5.5-5.6），在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\n\n[375 more lines in file. Use offset=243 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780248512461}}
{"type":"message","id":"4060f1b7","parentId":"8c83edf6","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:28:42.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK now I see the problem. The section header for 3.4 is gone, and the cron flow for stench_number got merged with the morningcourt section. Let me rewrite the whole block from 3.3 to just before 3.5.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zmy1CGoy23380G1ZiSXL1991","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"oldText":"### 3.3 调用已注册功能流程（两套路由）\n\n```\n触发: trigger_prompt.md 命中非 /菜单 /注册 /删除 的触发词\n\n→ 查 trigger_prompt.md「模式」列：\n  │\n  ├─ ⚡ 直连（秒回）─────────────\n  │   Step 1: spawn Son\n  │     sessions_spawn(agentId: \"son\", task: \"{...}\")\n  │   Step 2: sessions_yield 等结果\n  │   Step 3: 转话给用户\n  │\n  └─ ⏰ cron（耗时操作）──────────\n      Step 1: 回复用户```\n触发: session 收到格式为 [morningcourt] sender_id=xxx, trigger briefing generation 的消息\n\nStep 1: 识别模式\n  → 消息以 [morningcourt] 开头 → 早朝官 cron 触发\n  → 提取 sender_id\n\nStep 2: spawn Son\n  → sessions_spawn(\n      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: '{\"function\":\"morningcourt\",\"action\":\"manual\",\"params\":{\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}'\n    )\n\nStep 3: 等 Son 结果\n  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 主动话题推送","newText":"### 3.3 调用已注册功能流程（两套路由）\n\n```\n触发: trigger_prompt.md 命中非 /菜单 /注册 /删除 的触发词\n\n→ 查 trigger_prompt.md「模式」列：\n  │\n  ├─ ⚡ 直连（秒回）─────────────\n  │   直接 spawn Son 等结果\n  │   spawn Son → yield → 转话给用户\n  │\n  ├─ ⏰ cron（耗时操作）──────────\n  │   建一次性cron，不卡主session\n  │   1. 回复用户\"在搞了😏\"\n  │   2. 建一次性cron：\n  │      cron.add({\n  │        name: \"func-xxx-数字\",\n  │        schedule: {kind: \"at\", at: \"now+1s\"},\n  │        payload: {kind: \"agentTurn\", message: \"任务内容\", timeoutSeconds: 120},\n  │        agentId: \"son\",\n  │        delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"qqbot\", accountId: \"bot1\", to: \"qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}\"},\n  │        deleteAfterRun: true\n  │      })\n  │   3. 完事，不等\n  │\n  └─ 📋 管理（菜单/注册/删除）────\n      走 Spirit 流程\n```\n\n**不再呼叫 Spirit。** 日常使用 I／O 路径缩短为：Father → Son → Father → 用户。\n\n### 3.4 处理 cron 定时任务（如早朝官）\n\n```\n触发: session 收到格式为 [morningcourt] sender_id=xxx, trigger briefing generation 的消息\n\nStep 1: 识别模式\n  → 消息以 [morningcourt] 开头 → 早朝官 cron 触发\n  → 提取 sender_id\n\nStep 2: spawn Son\n  → sessions_spawn(\n      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: '{\"function\":\"morningcourt\",\"action\":\"manual\",\"params\":{\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}'\n    )\n\nStep 3: 等 Son 结果\n  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 主动话题推送","newTextShadow":"### 3.3 调用已注册功能流程（两套路由）\n\n```\n触发: trigger_prompt.md 命中非 /菜单 /注册 /删除 的触发词\n\n→ 查 trigger_prompt.md「模式」列：\n  │\n  ├─ ⚡ 直连（秒回）─────────────\n  │   Step 1: spawn Son\n  │     sessions_spawn(agentId: \"son\", task: \"{...}\")\n  │   Step 2: sessions_yield 等结果\n  │   Step 3: 转话给用户\n  │\n  ├─ ⏰ cron（耗时操作）──────────\n  │   Step 1: 回复用户\"在搞了😏\"\n  │   Step 2: 建一次性cron\n  │     cron.add({\n  │       name: \"func-xxx-数字\",\n  │       schedule: {kind: \"at\", at: \"now\"},\n  │       payload: {kind: \"agentTurn\", message: \"任务内容\", timeoutSeconds: 120},\n  │       agentId: \"son\",\n  │       delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"qqbot\", accountId: \"bot1\", to: \"qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}\"},\n  │       deleteAfterRun: true\n  │     })\n  │   Step 3: 完事，不等\n  │\n  └─ 📋 管理（菜单/注册/删除）────\n      走 Spirit 流程\n```\n\n### 3.4 处理 cron 定时任务（如早朝官）\n\n```\n触发: session 收到格式为 [morningcourt] sender_id=xxx, trigger briefing generation 的消息\n\nStep 1: 识别模式\n  → 消息以 [morningcourt] 开头 → 早朝官 cron 触发\n  → 提取 sender_id\n\nStep 2: spawn Son\n  → sessions_spawn(\n      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: '{\"function\":\"morningcourt\",\"action\":\"manual\",\"params\":{\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}'\n    )\n\nStep 3: 等 Son 结果\n  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 主动话题推送"}],"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"edits\": [{\"