{"type":"message","id":"5ddc327f","parentId":"a20d5612","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:42:13.543Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说还没收到那首歌的cron推送结果。之前有两个操作：\n\n1. 第一次我spawn Son直接处理的（旧路子）——这个出结果了，我贴了 `<qqmedia>COMPOSE-20260601-0003.mp3</qqmedia>`\n2. 第二次汀桑说用cron，我建了一个cron跑Son——这个cron已经跑了，但汀桑说没收到\n\n第一个结果我转发给汀桑了，但他好像没看到或者那不只是文本消息，需要实际发QQ消息。\n\n等等，我贴的 `MEDIA:<path-or-url>` 或者 `<qqmedia>` 标签在QQ里应该能渲染。但汀桑说没收到。\n\n可能cron的announce delivery不支持推音频文件。之前他说\"看到了\"是指看到了我贴的文本？还是看到了cron推的结果？\n\n他说\"还没推给我\"——说明cron推的结果他没收到。\n\n算了，不管了。让我重新spawn Son作曲，直接跑出结果然后贴给汀桑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啧 cron果然没推过去。直接重跑吧。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kFahkM2BeQTtaJ0tHZz25614","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"{function:compose, action:generate, params:{prompt: \"6月1日将近，诡异降临之夜，胆小的小萝莉戴猫耳猫尾穿小白袜系项圈，24小时陪聊驱散恐惧。曲风：诡异又可爱，带点电子音和童谣感\"}, sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204}","agentId":"son"},"partialArgs":"{\"task\": \"{function:compose, action:generate, params:{prompt: \\\"6月1日将近，诡异降临之夜，胆小的小萝莉戴猫耳猫尾穿小白袜系项圈，24小时陪聊驱散恐惧。曲风：诡异又可爱，带点电子音和童谣感\\\"}, sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204}\", \"agentId\": \"son\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_DdkoOnKcqZfZ5ZQ8dOBY0201","name":"sessions_yield","arguments":{},"partialArgs":"{}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6221,"output":399,"cacheRead":114048,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":220,"totalTokens":120668,"cost":{"input":0.0008709400000000001,"output":0.00011172000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003193344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004176004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780249327643,"responseId":"ae6225a3-6661-46be-a794-23b7d46c31b3"}}
