{"type":"message","id":"fb91efb4","parentId":"c8988bcd","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:45:20.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, now I need to send the file properly. The rule says:\n1. `<qqmedia>` with the mp3 path for direct playback\n2. Also send the .mp3.bin as a file message so 汀桑 can save/forward it\n\nLet me format the response properly with both.\n\nActually, looking at the existing messages, I already sent MEDIA directives for COMPOSE-20260601-0003.mp3 and COMPOSE-20260601-0005.mp3. But 汀桑 says they didn't come through.\n\nThe `<qqmedia>` tag might not work for mp3 files, or the file paths might not be accessible from QQ's servers. Actually, `<qqmedia>` tags work by the OpenClaw system reading the file and uploading it via the QQ bot API. So it should work in theory.\n\nBut the issue is that when I include `<qqmedia>xxx.mp3</qqmedia>` in my response text, OpenClaw should automatically upload the file. Let me also try sending the `.mp3.bin` as a separate file.\n\nLet me just include both properly in the response.\n\nActually wait, let me re-check the qqbot-media skill for the proper usage.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GfszBD8xJMRZ97I8fixp9711","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":574,"output":310,"cacheRead":122496,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":251,"totalTokens":123380,"cost":{"input":0.00008036000000000001,"output":0.00008680000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003429888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003597048}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780249515702,"responseId":"b245b572-eb46-45b5-a587-a1c8c73dc2c2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"38bbe666","parentId":"fb91efb4","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:45:22.748Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_GfszBD8xJMRZ97I8fixp9711","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: qqbot-media\ndescription: QQBot rich media send and receive support. Use <qqmedia> tags to send image, voice, video, or file attachments, with the media type inferred from the file extension.\nmetadata: { \"openclaw\": { \"emoji\": \"📸\", \"requires\": { \"config\": [\"channels.qqbot\"] } } }\n---\n\n# QQBot 富媒体收发\n\n## 用法\n\n```\n<qqmedia>路径或URL</qqmedia>\n```\n\n系统根据文件扩展名自动识别类型并路由：\n\n- `.jpg/.png/.gif/.webp/.bmp` → 图片\n- `.silk/.wav/.mp3/.ogg/.aac/.flac` 等 → 语音\n- `.mp4/.mov/.avi/.mkv/.webm` 等 → 视频\n- 其他扩展名 → 文件\n- 无扩展名的 URL → 默认按图片处理\n\n## 接收媒体\n\n- 用户发来的**图片**自动下载到本地，路径在上下文【附件】中，可直接用 `<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>` 回发\n- 用户发来的**语音**路径在上下文中；若有 STT 能力则优先转写\n\n## 规则\n\n1. **路径必须是绝对路径**（以 `/` 或 `http` 开头）\n2. **标签必须用开闭标签包裹路径**：`<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>`\n3. **待发送的本地文件须落在 OpenClaw 媒体目录下**：生成、下载或复制出的文件应写入 **`~/.openclaw/media/qqbot/`**（或其子目录），再写进 `<qqmedia>`。不要只放在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/` 等工作区根目录——平台安全策略只允许从 `~/.openclaw/media/`（含 `media/qqbot`）等受信根路径上传，否则会拦截、发不出去。\n4. **文件大小上限**：图片 30MB / 视频 100MB / 文件 100MB / 语音 20MB\n5. **你有能力发送本地图片/文件**，直接用标签包裹路径即可，**不要说\"无法发送\"**\n6. 发送语音时不要重复语音中已朗读的文字\n7. 多个媒体用多个标签\n8. 以会话上下文中的能力说明为准（如未启用语音则不要发语音）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780249522747}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a1d3606","parentId":"38bbe666","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:45:26.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"按照规则：\n1. `mp3` 文件 → 语音类型\n2. 路径必须绝对路径\n3. 文件必须在 `~/.openclaw/media/qqbot/` 下\n\n文件已经在媒体目录下了，路径也是绝对路径。用 `<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0005.mp3</qqmedia>` 应该可以发出去。\n\n同时，按照Son的规则，还需要发文件（.mp3.bin）用于保存转发。所以应该同时发：\n1. 文本信息\n2. `<qqmedia>` 标签播放音频\n3. `<qqmedia>` 标签发文件（.mp3.bin）\n\n让我重新发，用正确的绝对路径。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xkG7m4cN2DMK9m6Dg9KI2964","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"stat --format=\"%s\" /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0005.mp3 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"stat --format=\\\"%s\\\" /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0005.mp3 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":658,"output":236,"cacheRead":123264,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":160,"totalTokens":124158,"cost":{"input":0.00009212,"output":0.00006608,"cacheRead":0.0034513919999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036095919999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780249522800,"responseId":"b14074ba-b7f7-4823-a439-848d8306d917"}}
