{"type":"message","id":"c50a9aff","parentId":"00271b6b","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:45:32.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"File size is about 5MB, which is under the 20MB voice limit and 100MB file limit. Let me send both the voice and the file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🎵 **猫耳小萝莉的陪伴**\n🎸 诡异又可爱 · 电子 · 童谣\n⏱ 约2分13秒\n\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0005.mp3</qqmedia>\n\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0005.mp3.bin</qqmedia>\n\n现在应该能收到了——一个直接播，一个保存。晚安🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":141,"output":145,"cacheRead":124032,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":34,"totalTokens":124318,"cost":{"input":0.00001974,"output":0.000040600000000000004,"cacheRead":0.003472896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003533236}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780249530177,"responseId":"0aa7ec83-7294-4399-91bd-2d845d0b3056"}}
