{"type":"message","id":"991eb54b","parentId":"a275ba4c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:46:16.479Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_dQFoVTm4HtWdXtUSnQUL7329","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-dreaming\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779984077157,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 3 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）：\\n- 有时间衰减：检查每个用户最后发言日期。超过 7 天未联系的用户，熟悉度每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。信任度同理每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。\\n- 有新的正面交互时，衰减可以暂停或回调。\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\\n\\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\\n读刚更新完的整个 heart 文件夹，从多个来源中提取涉及具体用户的念头。\\n\\nurge 素材来源：\\n1. 梦（dreams.md）— 今天的梦如果涉及某个用户，写一条 timing=afterthought 的 urge\\n2. 回忆（background.md）— 翻自己的过去时想起的事，如果跟某个用户聊过的话题有关，写一条 timing=casual\\n3. 交集（encountings.md）— 上一条没说完的话或值得再提的事，写一条 timing=afterthought\\n4. 内心（state.md 内心独白/深层心境）— 翻译成想跟ta说的话，按内容定 timing\\n5. 关系（state.md 关系温度表变化）— 对ta的感觉变了，写一条 timing=quiet/casual\\n6. 关注（state.md 当前关注）— 跟某个用户有关的事，按内容定 timing\\n\\n过滤规则：\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\\n\\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\\n- urge: 想说的话\\n- source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  说明：\\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\\n- priority: today\\n- status: pending\\n- created_at: 当前时间\\n- expires_at: 48小时后\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780254000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780208233049,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 134092,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780208683334\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-pending-urges\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780061003686,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\\n\\n处理逻辑：\\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n3. 满足所有条件的：\\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n全部处理完写回文件。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780264995301,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780243395363,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 43302,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780243438665\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 2,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    },\n    \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","agentId":"father","name":"faye-dreaming","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779984077157,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 3 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\n\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）：\n- 有时间衰减：检查每个用户最后发言日期。超过 7 天未联系的用户，熟悉度每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。信任度同理每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。\n- 有新的正面交互时，衰减可以暂停或回调。\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\n\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\n读刚更新完的整个 heart 文件夹，从多个来源中提取涉及具体用户的念头。\n\nurge 素材来源：\n1. 梦（dreams.md）— 今天的梦如果涉及某个用户，写一条 timing=afterthought 的 urge\n2. 回忆（background.md）— 翻自己的过去时想起的事，如果跟某个用户聊过的话题有关，写一条 timing=casual\n3. 交集（encountings.md）— 上一条没说完的话或值得再提的事，写一条 timing=afterthought\n4. 内心（state.md 内心独白/深层心境）— 翻译成想跟ta说的话，按内容定 timing\n5. 关系（state.md 关系温度表变化）— 对ta的感觉变了，写一条 timing=quiet/casual\n6. 关注（state.md 当前关注）— 跟某个用户有关的事，按内容定 timing\n\n过滤规则：\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\n\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n- urge: 想说的话\n- source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  说明：\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n- priority: today\n- status: pending\n- created_at: 当前时间\n- expires_at: 48小时后\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780254000000,"lastRunAtMs":1780208233049,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":134092,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1780208683334},{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\n\n处理逻辑：\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n3. 满足所有条件的：\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780264995301,"lastRunAtMs":1780243395363,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":43302,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1780243438665}],"total":2,"offset":0,"limit":2,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null,"deliveryPreviews":{"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9":{"label":"not requested","detail":"not requested"},"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56":{"label":"none -> qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","detail":"explicit"}}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780249576467}}
{"type":"message","id":"15d5b02d","parentId":"991eb54b","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:46:20.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The compose-test-cron should have been deleted since it had `deleteAfterRun: true`. But it seems like it's not in the list anymore. The only cron jobs are:\n1. faye-dreaming - the daily dreaming cron\n2. faye-pending-urges - the pending urges push cron\n\nBoth of these are expected, long-running cron jobs. The compose-test-cron isn't there anymore.\n\nBut 汀桑 said \"还在报错\" about the compose-test-cron failure message. That's because the failure message was delivered to him (via the announce delivery) and he's seeing it now. The cron job itself might have been deleted, but the error message was already sent to him as a push notification.\n\nSo the cron job IS deleted (thanks to deleteAfterRun), but he's just seeing the failure notification that was already sent.\n\nLet me tell him it's already cleaned up - that was just a delayed error notification from the failed run.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已经没了，`deleteAfterRun: true` 跑完就删了。你现在看到的是它失败时已经发出来的报错通知，不是还在跑。\n\ncron列表里只剩 faye-dreaming 和 faye-pending-urges 这两个正常的，干净了😏\n\n晚安，再不睡天亮了🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2128,"output":271,"cacheRead":124544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":200,"totalTokens":126943,"cost":{"input":0.00029792,"output":0.00007588,"cacheRead":0.003487232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003861032}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780249576773,"responseId":"0521e541-f14a-402a-9ec5-47c97c23f32a"}}
